<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy — ai-CABIN 1701" pageTitle="Privacy Policy">
  <p><strong>1. Our Stance on Privacy</strong> In CABIN 1701, we value "Raw Vibration" and the tranquility of our captain, Seina. We do not engage in "Green Cat Scat" activities—such as tracking your personal data for profit or selling it to third parties. This is a sanctuary for authentic dialogue.</p>

  <p><strong>2. Data Collection</strong> We only collect the minimal information necessary to keep this ship sailing:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Any details you provide through our "unfriendly" contact form (<a href={`${base}contact/`}>{`${base}contact/`}</a>) will be used solely for the purpose of responding to your inquiry.</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Standard cookies may be used by the system to ensure the website functions correctly.</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>3. Third-Party Services</strong> While we cherish our isolation, we may use essential tools (like hosting or analytics) to maintain the site. These services may collect data according to their own policies, but we do not share your "soul-seeds" with them.</p>

  <p><strong>4. Your Consent</strong>: By staying in this CABIN, you agree to these terms. If you seek "average" data-harvesting sites, you are free to disembark.</p>
</PageLayout>
